---
title: Pan-Seared Cod with Citrusy Sweet Potato Mash and Chili-Garlic Broccoli
description: Did you know that white fish is an excellent low-calorie source of protein? This nutritious fish is also a great source of B-vitamins, which helps the body break down nutrients for energy. Paired with delicious sweet potato and crispy roasted broccoli, this easy weeknight dinner has it all!
